EXACTLY.

03:14.695 --> 03:16.530
- THAT'S WHAT IT'S LIKE.
- OH, THAT'S HORRIBLE.

03:16.630 --> 03:18.732
- YOU KNOW WHAT? YOU KNOW
WHAT THE WORST PART IS?
- WHAT?

03:18.832 --> 03:20.901
WE'RE WAITING
FOR THE RESULTS
OF THIS BIOPSY NOW.

03:21.001 --> 03:24.305
I GOT ABOUT 24 HOURS
TO GET OUT OF THIS THING
BEFORE THE RESULTS COME BACK.

03:24.405 --> 03:26.274
YEAH, YOU CAN'T BREAK UP
WITH SOMEBODY WHO'S GOT CANCER.

03:26.374 --> 03:29.377
YOU GOTTA BREAK UP
WITH HER BEFORE SHE GETS
THOSE TEST RESULTS.

03:29.477 --> 03:31.745
( sighs )
GOD, IT'S GONNA BE SO HARD.

03:31.845 --> 03:34.482
- WHY? WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN "WHAT'S
THE BIG DEAL?"

03:34.582 --> 03:36.484
THE WHOLE FAMILY'S GOTTA
MOVE OUT-- IT'S A BIG DEAL!

03:36.584 --> 03:39.253
I'D MUCH RATHER BE
IN HER POSITION THAN MINE
ANY DAY OF THE WEEK.

03:39.353 --> 03:41.322
NO, TO BE THE BREAKER-UPPER
YOU'RE IN CONTROL.

03:41.422 --> 03:43.991
COUPLES SHOULD HAVE LIKE
A PRE-BREAKUP AGREEMENT

03:44.091 --> 03:47.495
BEFORE THEY START GOING OUT
BECAUSE EVERY RELATIONSHIP IS
GOING TO END AT SOME POINT.

03:47.595 --> 03:49.530
ALL YOU DO IS SEND A TEXT.
YOU MAKE AN AGREEMENT--

03:49.630 --> 03:51.799
"IF YOU SEE THE WORD 'APRICOT,'
IT MEANS IT'S OVER."

03:51.899 --> 03:55.736
OKAY, HYPOTHETICALLY,
WHAT IF YOU OR SHE ARE
EATING APRICOTS AT THAT POINT?

03:55.836 --> 03:58.105
- CAN I TELL YOU SOMETHING
ABOUT APRICOTS?
- WHAT WHAT?

03:58.205 --> 04:00.741
YOU KNOW, ONE IN 30
IS A GOOD ONE.

04:00.841 --> 04:03.143
- OKAY.
- IT'S SUCH
A LOW-PERCENTAGE FRUIT.

04:03.243 --> 04:04.945
- OKAY.
- ALWAYS A MEALY DRY--

04:05.045 --> 04:06.380
- HEY, HOW'S IT GOING?
- HEY.

04:06.480 --> 04:08.382
- HI, LAR.
- OH, HEY.

04:08.482 --> 04:10.784
- HEY.
- WANT TO COME TO
A DINNER PARTY TONIGHT?

04:10.884 --> 04:12.553
- TONIGHT?
- YEAH.

04:12.653 --> 04:14.788
- OH.
- YOU KNOW YOU LOVE
MY COOKING.

04:14.888 --> 04:17.291
IT'S A LITTLE LATE
FOR AN INVITATION,
IS IT NOT?

04:17.391 --> 04:19.660
WELL... IT'S AN INVITATION
NONETHELESS.

04:19.760 --> 04:22.630
- WHO ELSE IS GONNA BE THERE?
- UH, EH, YOU DON'T
NEED TO KNOW.

04:22.730 --> 04:25.799
- WHY NOT?
- BECAUSE IT'S NOT DONE,
THAT'S WHY NOT.

04:25.899 --> 04:29.002
- WHAT DO YOU
MEAN IT'S NOT DONE?
- IT'S A SOCIAL CONVENTION

04:29.102 --> 04:32.506
THAT PEOPLE DON'T ASK
WHO'S GOING TO BE THERE
AT THE DINNER PARTY.

04:32.606 --> 04:34.875
- IT'S JUST NOT DONE.
- BIG DEAL. WHY ISN'T IT DONE?

04:34.975 --> 04:38.078
BECAUSE IT ISN'T!
I DON'T KNOW THE DERIVATION
OF THE CONVENTION.

04:38.178 --> 04:40.113
WHY ARE YOU FOLLOWING IT
BLINDLY LIKE THIS?

04:40.213 --> 04:41.949
YOU SHOULD BE GLAD
THAT IT HAPPENS THAT WAY,

04:42.049 --> 04:44.151
BECAUSE IF I TOLD
PEOPLE YOU WERE COMING,
THEY MIGHT NOT SHOW UP.

04:44.251 --> 04:47.220
THAT'S PROBABLY WHY
PEOPLE DON'T TELL-- BECAUSE IF
IT GETS OUT WHO'S COMING

04:47.321 --> 04:49.923
